--------------
- HLDS ERROR -
--------------

You must first install or locate the hldsupdatetool.exe.

Install:
1. Go to File -> Install Server -> HLDS Update Tool.
2. Follow the prompts from the installer.
3. Make sure you note the installtion location as you will need this for Servers to be installed.

Locate:
1. Browse or go to start -> search for hldsupdatetool.exe
2. Select the directory it is in and click ok.
